reviewText: Excellent source for 221 information and care.
Walks you through everything you would want to know.  Nice step by step instructions.
The best tool I have found for caring for my featherweight fleet... I also added a 301 to my machines due to the added streangth...

This video is a "Must Have" if you are the owner of a Featherweight. It has paid for itself already by teaching me how to maintain my machine instead of taking it in for service. The instruction is clear, consice and answered all my questions.
Thorough instructions including background on the Singer Featherweights.  You will be able to completely service your machine with guidance from this CD.

This is just what I was looking for...  Detailed instructions for maintaining and repairing your Singer Featherweight sewing machine!  I am excited to have this information at my fingertips whenever I might need it!

The day this DVD arrived it saved me more than its cost. I can now do maintenance and most repairs on the Featherweight myself and save the time and expence of taking the machine to a repair shop. The instructions for removing the smell and improving the appearance of the case made it possible to use the case and keep it indoors. The instructions for cleaning and shining make the machine look nearly new. This is a must DVD for Featherweight owners that would like to clean and maintain there own machines.
